-- FIX FILE: Teacher Dashboard + Semester Display
-- Problems Solved:
--   1. Teacher dashboard pe 5 sessions ek hi course ke
--      ROOT CAUSE: Duplicate sections ya sessions for same teacher
--   2. Reports mein semester properly show nahi hota
